NK037(ji)008:1: // dpal ldan mgon po'i gab thig 'khrugs kyi man ngag bzhugs so //
NK037(ji)008:2: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ya na mo /
NK037(ji)008:3: mgon po spyan ras gzigs dbang dang //
NK037(ji)008:4: chos skyong legs ldan sras po dang //
NK037(ji)008:5: phyogs bcu'i mgon po 'khor bcas dang //
NK037(ji)008:6: nag po gri gug thod khrag 'dzin //
NK037(ji)008:7: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs bcas la //
NK037(ji)008:8: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK037(ji)008:9: lnga brgya snyigs ma'i dus 'di la //
NK037(ji)008:10: bstan pa'i ru tra bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)008:11: sa bcu rdzogs pa'i legs ldan sras //
NK037(ji)008:12: ma h+aa k+aa la 'khor bcas kyi //
NK037(ji)008:13: sgrub thabs las kyi rim pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:14: snod med rnams la dkyus su sbas //
NK037(ji)008:15: snod ldan rnams kyi don du ni //
NK037(ji)008:16: gzhung gi man ngag gab thig rnams //
NK037(ji)008:17: bee ro tsa nas ci gsung bzhin //
NK037(ji)008:18: dbri bsnan med par gong 'og bsdebs //
NK037(ji)008:19: ldi ri chos grags yi ger bkod //
NK037(ji)008:24: lta spyod ldan pa'i rnal 'byor bas //
NK037(ji)008:26: shan pa mtshon thogs gcan gzan 'du //
NK037(ji)008:27: der ni man+dala legs par bya //
NK037(ji)008:28: gru gsum mthing nag kha khyer rtsang //
NK037(ji)008:29: dar nag snying dang bya rgod mda' //
NK037(ji)008:30: rab tu mnyes pa'i mchod gtor bsham //
NK037(ji)008:31: sgrub pa'i gtor ma bca' ba ni //
NK037(ji)008:32: snod mchog gang yang rung ba'i nang //
NK037(ji)008:33: bshos bu g.yag snying lta bu gcig /
NK037(ji)008:34: ngos gsum gtor ma gsum bshams la //
NK037(ji)008:35: gzugs 'gros sna tshogs dag gis bskor //
NK037(ji)008:36: bing ni ma h+aa k+aa la'i rten //
NK037(ji)008:37: rta nag snying dang dar nag sku yi rten //
NK037(ji)008:38: lug nag snying ni gsung gi rten //
NK037(ji)008:39: g.yag nag snying ni thugs kyi rten //
NK037(ji)008:40: mda' rgod rin chen sna lnga btags //
NK037(ji)008:41: dar sna la du la phug sna tshogs dang //
NK037(ji)008:42: sbrang chang khur ba sha thud la sogs dang //
NK037(ji)008:43: phyogs bcu mgon po'i rten du bzhag /
NK037(ji)008:44: gru gsum bang rim gsum pa'i steng //
NK037(ji)008:45: many+dzi'i steng du gtor ma bkyag /
NK037(ji)008:46: zhabs su gru gsum ling+ga bcug /
NK037(ji)008:47: khyi ra phag gsum thod pa'i nang du bcug /
NK037(ji)008:48: rgyab tu re 'byams rnams kyis bskor //
NK037(ji)008:51: ka de nas mdun bskyed 'jug pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:52: bdag nyid he ru ka'i nga rgyal bsgom //
NK037(ji)008:53: mdun du gru gsum mi dmigs stong pa'i ngang //
NK037(ji)008:54: gru gsum bang rim gsum pa'i nang //
NK037(ji)008:55: gru gsum dmar nag rab tu 'jigs //
NK037(ji)008:56: me ltar tsha zhing skyi g.ya' ba //
NK037(ji)008:57: nad kyi na bun rab tu 'khrigs //
NK037(ji)008:58: mtshon cha'i tsh+wa tsh+wa me ltar 'bar //
NK037(ji)008:59: chom chom sod sod sgra sgrog pa //
NK037(ji)008:60: gru gsum 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK037(ji)008:61: nang du nyi ma ro yi steng //
NK037(ji)008:62: bdag gi thugs ka'i sa bon las //
NK037(ji)008:63: yi ge h'u mthing phar 'phros pas //
NK037(ji)008:65: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs thams cad bsgral //
NK037(ji)008:67: bing de h'u gis mtshan pa las //
NK037(ji)008:68: mgon po tshogs bdag sku mdog mthing //
NK037(ji)008:69: char sprin lta bur rab tu 'jigs //
NK037(ji)008:70: dar nag 'jol ber sku la gsol //
NK037(ji)008:71: phyag g.yas tsan+dana bing chen phyar //
NK037(ji)008:72: g.yon pas thod pa khrag bkang gsol //
NK037(ji)008:73: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa //
NK037(ji)008:74: thod pa rin chen sbrul gyis brgyan //
NK037(ji)008:75: dar 'phyangs sbrul gyi ske rag bcings //
NK037(ji)008:76: sag ti sngon po'i chags lhwam mnabs //
NK037(ji)008:77: me rlung 'tshubs ma'i dbus na bzhugs //
NK037(ji)008:78: de yi g.yon du b+h+yohls ni //
NK037(ji)008:79: yum chen yak+sha be t+aa li /
NK037(ji)008:80: sku mdog nag mo 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK037(ji)008:81: g.yas g.yon gri gug thod khrag 'dzin //
NK037(ji)008:82: mgon po'i thugs kar h'u gsum 'phros //
NK037(ji)008:83: gru gsum bang rim dang po'i g.yas //
NK037(ji)008:84: mgon po sku mchog sngon po la //
NK037(ji)008:85: tri sh+aul rtse gsum thod khrag thogs //
NK037(ji)008:86: g.yon du mgon po gsung mchog dmar //
NK037(ji)008:87: phyag gnyis bing dang thod khrag thogs //
NK037(ji)008:88: mdun du mgon po thugs mchog mthing //
NK037(ji)008:89: phyag gnyis gri gug thod khrag bsnams //
NK037(ji)008:90: sku gsung thugs kyi mgon po rnams //
NK037(ji)008:91: rgyan dang chu lugs gtso dang mthun //
NK037(ji)008:92: nag po stod dang sha za 'bum //
NK037(ji)008:93: ma mo bye ba'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK037(ji)008:94: gru gsum bang rim bar ma la //
NK037(ji)008:95: lha dmag bye ba dung phyur bskor //
NK037(ji)008:96: go mtshon mang po lus la brgyan //
NK037(ji)008:97: gru gsum tha mar bka' sdod tshogs //
NK037(ji)008:98: dri za me lha gshin rje dang //
NK037(ji)008:99: bden bral chu bdag rlung gi lha //
NK037(ji)008:100: gnod sbyin dbang ldan sa bdag dang //
NK037(ji)008:101: nyi zla gza' skar tshogs dang bcas //
NK037(ji)008:102: sprul pa yang sprul phra men tshogs //
NK037(ji)008:103: stag gzigs dom dang byi la dang //
NK037(ji)008:104: pha wam dred mong phag rgod dang //
NK037(ji)008:105: rnga mong sbal sbrul mgo brnyan can //
NK037(ji)008:106: thams cad 'jigs su rung ba'i gzugs //
NK037(ji)008:107: bskal pa'i me dpung klong du bskyed //
NK037(ji)008:111: de nas bdag gi thugs ka nas //
NK037(ji)008:113: ri rab dag gi byang shar mtshams //
NK037(ji)008:114: rang bzhin gnas nas ye shes pa //
NK037(ji)008:116: sh+r+ai ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya phem phem /
NK037(ji)008:118: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i dbus //
NK037(ji)008:119: gnam lcags ur mo ta la la //
NK037(ji)008:120: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho me te re //
NK037(ji)008:121: zhing chen keng rus khra la la //
NK037(ji)008:122: 'dab chags mang po nyi li li //
NK037(ji)008:123: zhing lpags g.yang gzhi lhubs se lhub //
NK037(ji)008:124: gsur chen dud pa chi li li //
NK037(ji)008:126: mgon po 'khor bcas sku skyod cig /
NK037(ji)008:128: mgon po tshogs bdag 'khor bcas rnams //
NK037(ji)008:129: dam tshig dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK037(ji)008:130: e h+ye hi sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la g+ha na
NK037(ji)008:131: g+hu ti ka ma la s+r+ai nag mo ting lam
NK037(ji)008:132: b+h+yo / sa ma ya dzahmh'u bam hoh sa ma ya /
NK037(ji)008:134: ga bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK037(ji)008:136: bdud 'dul tshogs bdag chen po ste //
NK037(ji)008:137: rdo rje skul byed drag po rtsal //
NK037(ji)008:138: srin po lang ka pu ri yi //
NK037(ji)008:139: grong khyer chen po brlagsa mdzad cing //
NK037(ji)008:140: lha ma srin gyi bu mo ni //
NK037(ji)008:141: glog sprin 'dul bar zhal bzhes pa //
NK037(ji)008:142: lha chen mgon po nag po khyod //
NK037(ji)008:144: rdo rje 'chang gi spyan lnga ru //
NK037(ji)008:145: khas blangs dam bca' ma g.yel bar //
NK037(ji)008:147: dgyes shis brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK037(ji)008:148: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la g+ha na g+hu ti ka ma la sh+r+ai nag mo ting lam b+h+yo /
NK037(ji)008:149: tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK037(ji)008:153: nga mdun gyi gtor ma mi dmigs pa'i ngang las /
NK037(ji)008:154: sngags drug phyag drug gis byin gyis brlabs la 'bul /
NK037(ji)008:157: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK037(ji)008:158: mgon po 'khor dang bcas pas ljags rdo rje'i sbu gus gsol bar bsam /
NK037(ji)008:159: mnyes shing tshims nas ci bcol ba'i phrin las rnam bzhi sgrub par bsam mo //
NK037(ji)008:161: bka' yi bstan srung zhal bzhes pa //
NK037(ji)008:162: bdud 'dul ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)008:163: nag po chen po 'khor bcas la //
NK037(ji)008:164: mnyam nyid kun tu bzang po'i klong //
NK037(ji)008:165: gnyis med mchod pa'i bye brag shar //
NK037(ji)008:166: yon chab me tog bdug spos dang //
NK037(ji)008:167: mar me dri chab zhal zas dang //
NK037(ji)008:168: rol mo la sogs mchod pa'i tshogs //
NK037(ji)008:170: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la ar+g+ham p+aa d+yam nas /
NK037(ji)008:171: shap+da g+airti sa ma ya mu dra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK037(ji)008:173: lcang lor bcas pa'i b+han+d+ha ru //
NK037(ji)008:174: byang sems dkar dmar rak+ta dang //
NK037(ji)008:175: dri chen gur gum bdud rtsi ste //
NK037(ji)008:176: gnyis med bdud rtsi a mri ta //
NK037(ji)008:177: ye shes bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'di //
NK037(ji)008:179: sh+ri ma h+aa k+aa la sarba pany+tsa a mri ta rak+ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)008:182: mun pa nag po'i brda mi 'phrad //
NK037(ji)008:183: mgyogs byed dpa' bo rlung la zhon //
NK037(ji)008:186: dam nyams dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK037(ji)008:187: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la i dam ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK037(ji)008:191: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di /
NK037(ji)008:193: dpal ldan mgon po nag po /
NK037(ji)008:196: dug gsum nad kyi sman pa /
NK037(ji)008:199: dbus kyi de ba mgon po /
NK037(ji)008:200: phyi nang gnyis kyi tshogs bdag /
NK037(ji)008:202: sku gsung thugs kyi mgon po /
NK037(ji)008:208: lha dmag bye ba dung phyur dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul lo //
NK037(ji)008:213: bzhes rab kyi phul du gyur nas 'dod pa'i yon tan gyis mnyes shing tshim par mdzod la /
NK037(ji)008:214: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la bsrung zhing bskyab pa dang /
NK037(ji)008:215: bsam pa dang smon pa thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK037(ji)008:216: phrin las su bcol ba'i mdo ni /
NK037(ji)008:217: nyi ma phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad nas dgra bgegs gdug pa can sdang sems dang ldan pa rnams la /
NK037(ji)008:218: dam tshig gi dmod pa thong /
NK037(ji)008:221: sgyu ma'i lnga phung rdul du rlog /
NK037(ji)008:222: dgra bgegs thal ba'i rdul phran bzhin du brlag pa'i phrin las mdzod cig /
NK037(ji)008:225: de ni gtor ma 'bul ba lags so //
NK037(ji)008:228: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK037(ji)008:229: bstan pa bsrung bar sems bskyed pa //
NK037(ji)008:230: dpal ldan mgon po nag po ni //
NK037(ji)008:231: shin tu mi bzad 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK037(ji)008:232: yang dag dpa' bo chen po la //
NK037(ji)008:233: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa //
NK037(ji)008:234: mgon po nag po khyed la bstod //
NK037(ji)008:235: dar nag 'jol ber mnabs pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:236: nyon mongs bdud las rgyal ba'i rtags //
NK037(ji)008:237: tsan+dana bing chen bsnams pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:238: lha min g.yul ngo zlog pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)008:239: gser sked rin chen bcings pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:240: rnal 'byor bar chad sel ba'i rtags //
NK037(ji)008:241: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:242: 'chi bdag gshin rje zlog pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)008:243: me dpung klong na bzhugs pa ni //
NK037(ji)008:244: nyon mongs bag chags sreg pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)008:245: bam chen steng na 'gying ba ni //
NK037(ji)008:246: sa bdag klu gnyan 'joms pa'i rtags //
NK037(ji)008:247: dgra 'dul nag po chen po la //
NK037(ji)008:249: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong //
NK037(ji)008:250: rdo rje brag chen gtams pa'i khri //
NK037(ji)008:251: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dbus //
NK037(ji)008:252: ral gri mda' mdung gshibs pa'i gur nang na //
NK037(ji)008:253: zhing chen bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK037(ji)008:254: dpal ldan nag po chen po ni //
NK037(ji)008:255: shin tu mi bzad 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK037(ji)008:256: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK037(ji)008:257: sku la dar nag ber chen gsol //
NK037(ji)008:258: ral pa ser nag kyi li li //
NK037(ji)008:259: spyan nas bskal pa'i me stag 'phro //
NK037(ji)008:261: zhal nas khrag gi rba klong 'khrugs //
NK037(ji)008:262: ljags ni drag po glog ltar 'khyugs //
NK037(ji)008:263: mche ba rno gdug dgra la gtsigs //
NK037(ji)008:264: gdug pa'i nga ro sod dang rgyob //
NK037(ji)008:265: zhabs gnyis gyad kyi 'dor stabs bgrad //
NK037(ji)008:266: phyag na tsan+dana bing chen bsnams //
NK037(ji)008:267: bing chen gnyan po dgra la gsor //
NK037(ji)008:269: ltas ngan sna tshogs dgra la thong //
NK037(ji)008:270: bing las mi nad ling dgu 'phros //
NK037(ji)008:271: nad kyi rkyal kha dgra la phob //
NK037(ji)008:272: nag po mthu chen khyod la bstod //
NK037(ji)008:273: b+h+yoh yum chen lha mo be t+aa li //
NK037(ji)008:274: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog sngo //
NK037(ji)008:275: g.yas g.yon gri gug thod khrag bsnams //
NK037(ji)008:276: chibs su drel nag gwa pa chibs //
NK037(ji)008:278: 'dir gshegs dam rdzas gtor ma bzhes //
NK037(ji)008:279: lus ngag yid gsum gus pas bstod //
NK037(ji)008:284: mgon po 'khor bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK037(ji)008:285: mgon po'i dkyil 'khor sgor zhugs nas //
NK037(ji)008:286: bdag ni ma rig lus ngag sems //
NK037(ji)008:287: nongs pa thams cad bzod par gsol //
NK037(ji)008:288: dam tshig gnyan po bsrung rgyu la //
NK037(ji)008:289: bka' ltar ma gyur rngo ma thogs //
NK037(ji)008:290: bsnyen sgrub phud dang gtor ma chag /
NK037(ji)008:291: rtsa ba yan lag chag nyams kun //
NK037(ji)008:292: mgon po'i tshogs la bzod par gsol //
NK037(ji)008:293: bstan srung mthu yi dngos grub stsol //
NK037(ji)008:294: yi dam rtse gcig bsgom rgyu la //
NK037(ji)008:295: ting 'dzin ma gsal nog por bskyed //
NK037(ji)008:296: bstan srung tshogs la bzod bdag gis ma tshor nyams srid pas //
NK037(ji)008:297: phyin chad khyed kyis bzod bskang ngo bshags so bzod mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK037(ji)008:298: bskul cing dad cing mos pa'i tshe //
NK037(ji)008:299: ma g.yel las rnams myur 'grub mdzod //
NK037(ji)008:300: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)008:301: de nas sngags 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK037(ji)008:303: mgon po tshogs bdag yab yum dang //
NK037(ji)008:304: sku gsung thugs kyi mgon po dang //
NK037(ji)008:305: phyogs bcu mgon po'i thugs ka nas //
NK037(ji)008:306: nyi ma'i dbus su h'u mthing bsgom //
NK037(ji)008:307: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las ni //
NK037(ji)008:309: mgon po 'khor bcas thugs kar phog /
NK037(ji)008:310: ci bcol las rnams byed par bsam //
NK037(ji)008:311: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la h'u phata /
NK037(ji)008:312: badz+ra yak+sha be t+aa li h'u phata /
NK037(ji)008:313: ma h+aa k+aa la sid+d+hi yam du dzah sh+r+ai ma
NK037(ji)008:314: h+aa k+aa la gu na hri da k+aa ya w+aa
NK037(ji)008:315: ka tsit+ta gu na karma sarba h'u phata /
NK037(ji)008:322: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i dbus //
NK037(ji)008:323: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK037(ji)008:324: bam chen steng na 'gying bag can //
NK037(ji)008:325: dpal ldan mgon po nag po ni //
NK037(ji)008:326: bdud dang dgra bgegs bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)008:327: mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK037(ji)008:328: byams pa'i sems kyis mchod 'bul bstod //
NK037(ji)008:331: dpal ldan mgon po 'khor bcas rnams //
NK037(ji)008:332: bdag gis bsnyen cing bsgrubs pa la //
NK037(ji)008:333: thugs dang 'gal ba bzod par gsol //
NK037(ji)008:335: gnong 'gyod sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK037(ji)008:338: bdud 'dul tshogs bdag chen po dang //
NK037(ji)008:339: ma h+aa k+aa la 'jigs byed tshogs //
NK037(ji)008:340: rnal 'byor kun gyi dpal mgon te //
NK037(ji)008:341: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu rtsal can //
NK037(ji)008:342: rig 'dzin mang po'i srog shing ste //
NK037(ji)008:343: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dgra bla khyod //
NK037(ji)008:344: bdag gi chos skyong srung ma gyis //
NK037(ji)008:345: bdag gi dkon nor srung ba dang //
NK037(ji)008:346: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK037(ji)008:347: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK037(ji)008:348: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK037(ji)008:349: sarba sid+d+hi h+r+aih zhes yi ge brgya pas kha skong bya'o //
NK037(ji)008:352: rten 'brel snying pos mtha' rten bya'o //
NK037(ji)008:353: 'di yan chad stod las byang chub sgrub pa yin no //
NK037(ji)008:354: zhes sro thog rgyal ba'i dben gnas su chu mo
NK037(ji)008:355: glang lo'i nyer bdun la ldi ri chos kyi grags
